"The Greeks were highly successful in Hellenising various foreigners. During "
"the Hellenistic Age, Greek was the lingua franca of the Ancient World, "
"spoken widely from Spain to India."
msgstr "Los griegos tuvieron bastante éxito helenizando culturas extranjeras. Durante la era helenística el griego se convirtió en la lengua franca del mundo antiguo, ampliamente difundida desde Hispania hasta la lejana India. "

